stories.title: Pietersen century all in vain
stories.subTitle: South Africa v England, 5th ODI, East London
stories.summary: Kevin Pietersen's sensational 69-ball hundred, England's fastest in one-day cricket was not enough to save England from defeat in a thrilling fifth one-day international at East London
